		<title>07Recreation</title>
		<content> Since over 50% of the survey area     
 belongs to forestry or rough pasture, 
 recreation is limited.  There are no  
 facilities here such as cinemas, etc, 
 and for entertainment such as this,   
 people travel to either Aberdare or   
 further afield.  It could be said that
 most forms of entertainmet are based  
 around the home, with videos becoming 
 more popular than ever.  Videos are   
 found in many homes within the area.  
 Gardening remains a popular hobby,    
 along with pigeon racing.             
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
